mmunities; and \\par\nWhereas, The Borough Based Jails will enhance the well-being of uniformed and civilian staff, as well, through improved safety conditions, and\\par\nWhereas, The closure of Rikers Island, by establishing it as a public place subject to a use restriction that it shall not be used for incarceration of individuals after December 31, 2026, is critical to achieving the City\\rquote s criminal justice program goals and creating a more modern, humane and safe justice system; now, therefore be it\\par\n\\pard\\ltrpar\\fi720\\sl480\\slmult1\\qj Resolved, That the Council of the City of New York authorizes the filing of a land use application amending the City Map so as to establish a public place, with a use restriction, on the entirety of Rikers Island. \\i\\f1\\fs22  \\i0\\f0\\fs24\\par\n\\pard\\ltrpar\\qj\\fs20\\par\n\\par\n\\par\n\\par\n\\par\n\\par\nLS 12515\\par\n10/9/2019\\par\nJML/OGC\\f1\\fs22\\par\n\\pard\\ltrpar\\sa160\\sl252\\slmult1\\par\n}\n",
